## 3) Danh sach anh bat buoc can chup

### A. Anh khoi dong du an

1. Anh terminal sau khi chay `npm run dev` thanh cong.
   - Can thay thong tin server local dang chay.
2. Anh trang chu tai URL: `http://localhost:3000`
   - Can thay navbar, noi dung gioi thieu, nut dieu huong.

### B. Anh tung trang chuc nang

1. Trang Gioi thieu: `http://localhost:3000/about`
2. Trang Blog danh sach: `http://localhost:3000/blog`
3. Trang chi tiet bai viet hop le (vi du):
   - `http://localhost:3000/blog/gioi-thieu-nextjs`
4. Trang Du an: `http://localhost:3000/projects`
5. Trang Lien he: `http://localhost:3000/contact`

### C. Anh cac truong hop dac biet (quan trong)

1. Global 404 (khong ton tai route):
   - Mo URL: `http://localhost:3000/khong-ton-tai`
   - Chup man hinh hien "404" va nut "Ve trang chu".

2. Blog not-found theo slug:
   - Mo URL: `http://localhost:3000/blog/abc-xyz-khong-co`
   - Chup man hinh hien "Bai viet khong ton tai".

3. Blog loading:
   - Vao trang blog va chup skeleton loading.
   - Neu loading qua nhanh, mo DevTools -> Network -> chon Slow 3G roi refresh.

4. Blog error:
   - Cach de chup nhanh:
     - Tam thoi sua file `src/data/posts.ts`, doi ten ham `getPostBySlug` thanh sai (vi du: `getPostBySlugX`).
     - Luu file, mo lai trang blog detail de kich hoat trang error.
     - Chup man hinh co noi dung "Da xay ra loi!".
     - Hoan tac ngay thay doi vua sua de tra lai code dung.

### D. Anh build/deploy

1. Anh terminal build thanh cong:

```bash
npm run build
```

2. Neu ban da deploy (Vercel hoac nen tang khac), chup them:
   - Trang chu ban deployed (URL online).
   - 1 trang con bat ky (vi du /blog).

## 4) Tieu chi anh minh chung dat yeu cau

- URL hien ro tren thanh dia chi.
- Noi dung trang hien day du, khong bi cat mat phan quan trong.
- Co it nhat 1 anh terminal chay dev va 1 anh terminal build thanh cong.
- Anh loading/error/not-found phai la anh that tu du an.
- Thu tu file anh dung nhu checklist de de cham diem.

## 5) Muc nop bai de xuat

Nop kem:

1. Source code du an.
2. Thu muc `minh-chung-lab01` chua toan bo anh.
3. (Neu duoc yeu cau) file bao cao ngan 1-2 trang mo ta:
   - Cong nghe su dung
   - Cac route da lam
   - Cac truong hop loading, error, not-found
   - Link deploy

## 6) Kiem tra nhanh truoc khi nop

- Da chup du tat ca 13 anh trong checklist.
- Ten file anh dung chuan, de mo va de doi chieu.
- Khong con thay doi tam de test error trong source code.
- Du an chay lai binh thuong voi `npm run dev`.

Chuc ban nop bai suon se!